401 inline float getManhattanDistanceTo(float inX, float inY)
402 {
403 if (leftX < inX && inX <= rightX && bottomY < inY && inY <= topY)
404 {
405 return 0;
406 }
407 if (leftX < inX && inX <= rightX)
408 {
409 return std::min(std::fabs(inY - topY), std::fabs(inY - bottomY));
410 }
411 if (bottomY < inY && inY <= topY)
412 {
413 return std::min(std::fabs(inX - leftX), std::fabs(inX - rightX));
414 }
415 return std::min(std::fabs(inX - leftX), std::fabs(inX - rightX)) +
416 std::min(std::fabs(inY - topY), std::fabs(inY - bottomY));
417 }

580 inline float getRealUtilizationRate()
581 {
582 if (cells.size())
583 {
584 std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> cellVec;
585 cellVec.clear();
586 for (auto cell : cells)
587 {
588 cellVec.push_back(cell);
589 }
590 if (cellVec[0]->isLUT())
591 {
592 float tmputilization = 0;
593 for (auto cell : cells)
594 {
595 if (cell->isLUT6())
596 tmputilization += 2.0;
597 else
598 tmputilization += 1;
599 }
600 return (float)tmputilization / capacity;
601 }
602 else
603 {
604 return getUtilizationRate();
605 }
606 }
607 return 0;
608 }

1362 class PlacementUnpackedCell : public PlacementUnit

1364 public:
1372 PlacementUnpackedCell(std::string name, int id, DesignInfo::DesignCell *cell)
1373 : PlacementUnit(name, id, PlacementUnitType_UnpackedCell), cell(cell)
1374 {
1375 if (cell->isBRAM())
1376 addBRAM();
1377 if (cell->isDSP())
1378 addDSP();

1784 class PlacementNet

1786 public:
1794 PlacementNet(DesignInfo::DesignNet *designNet, int id, std::vector<PlacementUnit *> &cellId2PlacementUnitVec,
1795 PlacementInfo *placementInfo)
1796 : designNet(designNet), id(id), placementInfo(placementInfo)
1797 {
1798 unitsOfNetPins.clear();
1799 unitsOfDriverPins.clear();
1800 unitsOfPinsBeDriven.clear();
1801 PUSet.clear();
1802 for (DesignInfo::DesignPin *curPin : designNet->getPins())
1803 {
1804 PlacementUnit *tmpPU = cellId2PlacementUnitVec[curPin->getCell()->getElementIdInType()];
1805 unitsOfNetPins.push_back(tmpPU);
1806 PUSet.insert(tmpPU);
1807
1808 if (curPin->isOutputPort())
1809 {
1810 unitsOfDriverPins.push_back(tmpPU);
1811 }
1812 else
1813 {
1814 unitsOfPinsBeDriven.push_back(tmpPU);
1815 }
1816
1817 if (tmpPU->getType() == PlacementUnitType_UnpackedCell)
1818 {
1819 pinOffset tmpPinOffset = pinOffset(curPin->getOffsetXInCell(), curPin->getOffsetYInCell());
1820 pinOffsetsInUnit.push_back(tmpPinOffset);
1821 }
1822 else if (tmpPU->getType() == PlacementUnitType_Macro)
1823 {
1824 PlacementMacro *tmpM = dynamic_cast<PlacementMacro *>(tmpPU);
1825 assert(tmpM);
1826 pinOffset tmpPinOffset =
1827 pinOffset(curPin->getOffsetXInCell() + tmpM->getCellOffsetXInMacro(curPin->getCell()),
1828 curPin->getOffsetYInCell() + tmpM->getCellOffsetYInMacro(curPin->getCell()));
1829 pinOffsetsInUnit.push_back(tmpPinOffset);
1830 }
1831 }
1832 leftPuId = rightPuId = topPuId = bottomPuId = -1;
1833 }
1834 ~PlacementNet()
1835 {
1836 }

1914 inline bool updateNetBounds(bool updateX, bool updateY)
1915 {
1916 if (updateX)
1917 {
1918 leftPUX = 1e5;
1919 rightPUX = -1e5;
1920 leftPinX = 1e5;
1921 rightPinX = -1e5;
1922 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
1923 {
1924 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
1925 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
1926 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
1927 float cellX = tmpPU->X();
1928 float pinX = tmpPU->X() + tmpPinOffset.x;
1929 if (pinX < leftPinX)
1930 {
1931 leftPinX = pinX;
1932 leftPUX = cellX;
1933 leftPuId = tmpPUId;
1934 leftPinId_net = pinId_net;
1935 }
1936 if (pinX > rightPinX)
1937 {
1938 rightPinX = pinX;
1939 rightPUX = cellX;
1940 rightPuId = tmpPUId;
1941 rightPinId_net = pinId_net;
1942 }
1943 }
1944 }
1945 if (updateY)
1946 {
1947 topPUY = -1e5;
1948 bottomPUY = 1e5;
1949 topPinY = -1e5;
1950 bottomPinY = 1e5;
1951 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
1952 {
1953 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
1954 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
1955 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
1956 float cellY = tmpPU->Y();
1957 float pinY = tmpPU->Y() + tmpPinOffset.y;
1958 if (pinY < bottomPinY)
1959 {
1960 bottomPinY = pinY;
1961 bottomPUY = cellY;
1962 bottomPuId = tmpPUId;
1963 bottomPinId_net = pinId_net;
1964 }
1965 if (pinY > topPinY)
1966 {
1967 topPinY = pinY;
1968 topPUY = cellY;
1969 topPuId = tmpPUId;
1970 topPinId_net = pinId_net;
1971 }
1972 }
1973 }
1974 return (updateX && (leftPuId != rightPuId)) || (updateY && (topPuId != bottomPuId));
1975 }

1984 inline float getHPWL(float y2xRatio)
1985 {
1986 return std::fabs(rightPinX - leftPinX) + y2xRatio * std::fabs(topPinY - bottomPinY);

1988
2001 inline float getNewHPWLByTrying(PlacementUnit *curPU, double targetPUX, double targetPUY, float y2xRatio) const
2002 {
2003 float tmp_leftX = 1e5;
2004 float tmp_rightX = -1e5;
2005 float tmp_topY = -1e5;
2006 float tmp_bottomY = 1e5;
2007
2008 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2009 {
2010 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2011 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2012 float pinX;
2013 if (tmpPU == curPU)
2014 {
2015 pinX = targetPUX + tmpPinOffset.x;
2016 }
2017 else
2018 {
2019 pinX = tmpPU->X() + tmpPinOffset.x;
2020 }
2021 if (pinX < tmp_leftX)
2022 {
2023 tmp_leftX = pinX;
2024 }
2025 if (pinX > tmp_rightX)
2026 {
2027 tmp_rightX = pinX;
2028 }
2029 }
2030 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2031 {
2032 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2033 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2034 float pinY;
2035 if (tmpPU == curPU)
2036 {
2037 pinY = targetPUY + tmpPinOffset.y;
2038 }
2039 else
2040 {
2041 pinY = tmpPU->Y() + tmpPinOffset.y;
2042 }
2043 if (pinY < tmp_bottomY)
2044 {
2045 tmp_bottomY = pinY;
2046 }
2047 if (pinY > tmp_topY)
2048 {
2049 tmp_topY = pinY;
2050 }
2051 }
2052
2053 int A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX;
2054 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_rightX, tmp_bottomY, A_ClockRegionX,
2055 A_ClockRegionY);
2056 std::pair<int, int> A_ClockLocYX(A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX);
2057
2058 int B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX;
2059 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_leftX, tmp_topY, B_cellClockRegionX,
2060 B_cellClockRegionY);
2061 std::pair<int, int> B_ClockLocYX(B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX);
2062
2063 float clockRegionOverhead = 0;
2064 // if (B_ClockLocYX != A_ClockLocYX)
2065 // {
2066 // clockRegionOverhead = std::abs(B_cellClockRegionX - A_ClockRegionX) * 15;
2067 // }
2068
2069 return std::fabs(tmp_rightX - tmp_leftX) + y2xRatio * std::fabs(tmp_topY - tmp_bottomY) +
2070 clockRegionOverhead;
2071 }

2092 inline void updateBound2BoundNetWeight(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2093 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag,
2094 Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, float generalWeight, float y2xRatio,
2095 bool updateX, bool updateY, bool checkClockRegion = false)
2096 {
2097 assert(updateX ^ updateY);
2098 if (pinOffsetsInUnit.size() <= 1)
2099 return;
2100 float w = 2.0 * generalWeight / (float)(pinOffsetsInUnit.size() - 1);
2101 int nPins = pinOffsetsInUnit.size();
2102
2103 // adopt netDegree Weight from RippeFPGA
2104 if (nPins < 10)
2105 w *= 1.00;
2106 else if (nPins < 20)
2107 w *= 1.2;
2108 else if (nPins < 50)
2109 w *= 1.6;
2110 else if (nPins < 100)
2111 w *= 1.8;
2112 else if (nPins < 200)
2113 w *= 2.1;
2114 else
2115 w *= 2.5;
2116
2117 float tmp_rightX = getRightPinX(), tmp_bottomY = getBottomPinY(), tmp_leftX = getLeftPinX(),
2118 tmp_topY = getTopPinY();
2119
2120 int A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX;
2121 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_rightX, tmp_bottomY, A_ClockRegionX,
2122 A_ClockRegionY);
2123 std::pair<int, int> A_ClockLocYX(A_ClockRegionY, A_ClockRegionX);
2124
2125 int B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX;
2126 placementInfo->getDeviceInfo()->getClockRegionByLocation(tmp_leftX, tmp_topY, B_cellClockRegionX,
2127 B_cellClockRegionY);
2128 std::pair<int, int> B_ClockLocYX(B_cellClockRegionY, B_cellClockRegionX);
2129
2130 float clockRegionW = 0;
2131
2132 w *= designNet->getOverallEnhanceRatio();
2133 if (updateX)
2134 {
2135 if (checkClockRegion && B_cellClockRegionX != A_ClockRegionX)
2136 {
2137 clockRegionW = 1 + std::abs(B_cellClockRegionX - A_ClockRegionX) * 32 /
2138 (float)(pinOffsetsInUnit.size() - 1) * 0.01;
2139 if (clockRegionW > 3)
2140 clockRegionW = 3;
2141 // w *= clockRegionW;
2142 }
2143
2144 // add net between left node and right node
2145 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, leftPuId, rightPuId,
2146 leftPUX, rightPUX, pinOffsetsInUnit[leftPinId_net].x, pinOffsetsInUnit[rightPinId_net].x,
2147 !unitsOfNetPins[leftPinId_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[rightPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2148 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(leftPinId_net, rightPinId_net) * w /
2149 std::max(minDist, rightPinX - leftPinX));
2150
2151 // add net between internal node and left/right node
2152 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2153 {
2154 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2155 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2156 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2157 float curX = tmpPU->X();
2158 bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
2159 if (pinId_net != leftPinId_net && pinId_net != rightPinId_net)
2160 {
2161 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, leftPuId,
2162 curX, leftPUX, tmpPinOffset.x, pinOffsetsInUnit[leftPinId_net].x, movable,
2163 !unitsOfNetPins[leftPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2164 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, leftPinId_net) * w /
2165 std::max(minDist, (curX + tmpPinOffset.x) - leftPinX));
2166 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, rightPuId,
2167 curX, rightPUX, tmpPinOffset.x, pinOffsetsInUnit[rightPinId_net].x, movable,
2168 !unitsOfNetPins[rightPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2169 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, rightPinId_net) * w /
2170 std::max(minDist, rightPinX - (curX + tmpPinOffset.x)));
2171 }
2172 }
2173 }
2174 if (updateY)
2175 {
2176
2177 w *= y2xRatio;
2178
2179 // add net between top node and bottom node
2180 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, bottomPuId, topPuId,
2181 bottomPUY, topPUY, pinOffsetsInUnit[bottomPinId_net].y, pinOffsetsInUnit[topPinId_net].y,
2182 !unitsOfNetPins[bottomPinId_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[topPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2183 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(topPinId_net, bottomPinId_net) * w /
2184 std::max(minDist, topPinY - bottomPinY));
2185
2186 // add net between internal node and top/bottom node
2187 for (unsigned int pinId_net = 0; pinId_net < unitsOfNetPins.size(); pinId_net++)
2188 {
2189 auto tmpPU = unitsOfNetPins[pinId_net];
2190 auto tmpPUId = tmpPU->getId();
2191 auto tmpPinOffset = pinOffsetsInUnit[pinId_net];
2192 float curY = tmpPU->Y();
2193 bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
2194 if (pinId_net != topPinId_net && pinId_net != bottomPinId_net)
2195 {
2196 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, bottomPuId,
2197 curY, bottomPUY, tmpPinOffset.y, pinOffsetsInUnit[bottomPinId_net].y, movable,
2198 !unitsOfNetPins[bottomPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2199 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, bottomPinId_net) * w /
2200 std::max(minDist, (curY + tmpPinOffset.y) - bottomPinY));
2201 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPUId, topPuId,
2202 curY, topPUY, tmpPinOffset.y, pinOffsetsInUnit[topPinId_net].y, movable,
2203 !unitsOfNetPins[topPinId_net]->isFixed(),
2204 designNet->getPinPairEnhanceRatio(pinId_net, topPinId_net) * w /
2205 std::max(minDist, topPinY - (curY + tmpPinOffset.y)));
2206 }
2207 }
2208 }
2209 }

2211 inline void addPseudoNet_enhancePin2Pin(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2212 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag,
2213 Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, float generalWeight, float y2xRatio,
2214 bool updateX, bool updateY, int PUIdA, int PUIdB, int pinIdA_net,
2215 int pinIdB_net)
2216 {
2217 float w = generalWeight;
2218
2219 if (updateX)
2220 {
2221 // add net between left node and right node
2222 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, PUIdA, PUIdB,
2223 unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->X(), unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->X(),
2224 pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdA_net].x, pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdB_net].x,
2225 !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->isFixed(), w);
2226 }
2227 if (updateY)
2228 {
2229 w *= y2xRatio;
2230
2231 // add net between top node and bottom node
2232 addB2BNet(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, PUIdA, PUIdB,
2233 unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->Y(), unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->Y(),
2234 pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdA_net].y, pinOffsetsInUnit[pinIdB_net].y,
2235 !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdA_net]->isFixed(), !unitsOfNetPins[pinIdB_net]->isFixed(), w);
2236 }
2237 }

2261 inline void addB2BNet(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,
2262 std::vector<float> &objectiveMatrixDiag, Eigen::VectorXd &objectiveVector, int puId0,
2263 int puId1, float pos0, float pos1, float pinOffset0, float pinOffset1, bool movable0,
2264 bool movable1, float w)
2265 {
2266 // min_x 0.5 * x'Px + q'x
2267 // s.t. l <= Ax <= u
2268 if (puId0 == puId1)
2269 return;
2270 if (movable0 && movable1)
2271 {
2272 // x0^2 + x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2273 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
2274 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
2275 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
2276 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
2277 objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId1, -w));
2278 objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId0, -w));
2279 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2280 {
2281 // 2(x0c-x1c)x0 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2282 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
2283 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
2284 }
2285 }
2286 else if (movable0)
2287 {
2288 // x0^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x0c-x1c)x0
2289 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
2290 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
2291 objectiveVector[puId0] += -w * pos1;
2292 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2293 {
2294 // 2(x0c-x1c)x0
2295 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
2296 }
2297 }
2298 else if (movable1)
2299 {
2300 // x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2301 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
2302 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
2303 objectiveVector[puId1] += -w * pos0;
2304 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
2305 {
2306 // 2(x1c-x0c)x1
2307 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
2308 }
2309 }
2310 }

2907
2916 inline std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> *
2917 findNeiborLUTFFsFromBinGrid(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell, float displacementUpperbound, int minNumNeighbor = 10)
2918 {
2919 // please note that the input DesignCell is only used to find the corresponding binGrid for site search.
2920 bool findLUT = curCell->isLUT();
2921 float targetX = cellId2location[curCell->getCellId()].X;
2922 float targetY = cellId2location[curCell->getCellId()].Y;
2923 std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *> *res = new std::vector<DesignInfo::DesignCell *>();
2924 res->clear();
2925
2926 int binIdX, binIdY;
2927 getGridXY(targetX, targetY, binIdX, binIdY);
2928
2929 assert(binIdY >= 0);
2930 assert((unsigned int)binIdY < LUTFFBinGrid.size());
2931 assert(binIdX >= 0);
2932 assert((unsigned int)binIdX < LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY].size());
2933 assert(LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY][binIdX]->inRange(targetX, targetY));
2934
2935 std::queue<std::pair<int, int>> binXYqueue;
2936 std::set<std::pair<int, int>> reachedBinXYs;
2937 binXYqueue.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
2938 reachedBinXYs.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
2939
2940 bool findItself = false;
2941
2942 while (binXYqueue.size() > 0)
2943 {
2944 std::pair<int, int> curXY = binXYqueue.front();
2945 binXYqueue.pop();
2946 int curbinIdX = curXY.first, curbinIdY = curXY.second;
2947
2948 PlacementInfo::PlacementBinInfo *curBin = LUTFFBinGrid[curbinIdY][curbinIdX];
2949 float bin2TargetXYDistance = curBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
2950 if (bin2TargetXYDistance > displacementUpperbound)
2951 continue;
2952 for (auto tmpCell : curBin->getCells())
2953 {
2954 if ((tmpCell->isLUT() && findLUT) || (tmpCell->isFF() && !findLUT))
2955 {
2956 float tmpX = cellId2location[tmpCell->getCellId()].X;
2957 float tmpY = cellId2location[tmpCell->getCellId()].Y;
2958 float tmpPUDis = fabs(targetX - tmpX) + y2xRatio * fabs(targetY - tmpY);
2959 if (tmpPUDis <= displacementUpperbound)
2960 {
2961 if (tmpCell == curCell)
2962 {
2963 findItself = true;
2964 }
2965 res->push_back(tmpCell);
2966 }
2967 }
2968 }
2969 assert(findItself);
2970 for (int nextY = curbinIdY - 1; nextY <= curbinIdY + 1; nextY++)
2971 {
2972 for (int nextX = curbinIdX - 1; nextX <= curbinIdX + 1; nextX++)
2973 {
2974 if (!(nextY >= 0))
2975 continue;
2976 if (!((unsigned int)nextY < LUTFFBinGrid.size()))
2977 continue;
2978 if (!(nextX >= 0))
2979 continue;
2980 if (!((unsigned int)nextX < LUTFFBinGrid[binIdY].size()))
2981 continue;
2982 PlacementInfo::PlacementBinInfo *nextBin = LUTFFBinGrid[nextY][nextX];
2983 float nextBin2TargetXYDistance = nextBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
2984 if (nextBin2TargetXYDistance > displacementUpperbound)
2985 continue;
2986 std::pair<int, int> nextXY(nextX, nextY);
2987 if (reachedBinXYs.find(nextXY) == reachedBinXYs.end())
2988 {
2989 reachedBinXYs.insert(nextXY);
2990 binXYqueue.push(nextXY);
2991 }
2992 }
2993 }
2994 }
2995
2996 assert(findItself);
2997 return res;
2998 }

3061 inline void addB2BNetInPlacementInfo(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,

3073 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));

3076 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;

3082 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);
3083 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
3084 }
3085 }
3086 else if (movable0)
3087 {

3089 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId0, puId0, w));
3090 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId0] += w;
3091 objectiveVector[puId0] += -w * pos1;

3093 {

3095 objectiveVector[puId0] += w * (pinOffset0 - pinOffset1);

3098 else if (movable1)
3099 {
3100 // x1^2 - 2x0x1 + 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3101 // objectiveMatrixTripletList.push_back(Eigen::Triplet<float>(puId1, puId1, w));
3102 objectiveMatrixDiag[puId1] += w;
3103 objectiveVector[puId1] += -w * pos0;
3104 if (fabs(pinOffset0) > eps || fabs(pinOffset1) > eps)
3105 {
3106 // 2(x1c-x0c)x1
3107 objectiveVector[puId1] += w * (pinOffset1 - pinOffset0);
3108 }
3109 }
3110 }

3130 inline void addPseudoNetsInPlacementInfo(std::vector<Eigen::Triplet<float>> &objectiveMatrixTripletList,

3132 PlacementUnit *tmpPU, float targetLoc, float pseudoWeight, float y2xRatio,
3133 bool updateX, bool updateY)
3134 {
3135 assert(updateX ^ updateY);
3136 if (updateY)
3137 {
3138 pseudoWeight *= y2xRatio;
3139 }
3140 bool movable = !tmpPU->isFixed();
3141 if (movable)
3142 {
3143 addB2BNetInPlacementInfo(objectiveMatrixTripletList, objectiveMatrixDiag, objectiveVector, tmpPU->getId(),
3144 -1, targetLoc, targetLoc, 0, 0, true, false, pseudoWeight);

3694 inline std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *> *findNeiborSiteFromBinGrid(DesignInfo::DesignCell *curCell,
3695 float targetX, float targetY,
3696 float displacementThreshold,
3697 int siteNumThreshold)
3698 {
3699 // please note that the input DesignCell is only used to find the corresponding binGrid for site search.
3700 std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *> *res = new std::vector<DeviceInfo::DeviceSite *>(0);
3701
3702 int binIdX, binIdY;
3703 getGridXY(targetX, targetY, binIdX, binIdY);
3704
3705 while (res->size() == 0)
3706 {
3707 auto sharedTypeIds = getPotentialBELTypeIDs(curCell->getCellType());
3708
3709 for (auto sharedTypeId : sharedTypeIds)
3710 {
3711 assert((unsigned int)curCell->getCellId() < cellId2CellBinInfo.size());
3712 assert(binIdY >= 0);
3713 assert((unsigned int)binIdY < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId].size());
3714 assert(binIdX >= 0);
3715 assert((unsigned int)binIdX < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId][binIdY].size());
3716
3717 std::vector<std::vector<PlacementBinInfo *>> &curBinGrid = SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId];
3718
3719 std::queue<std::pair<int, int>> binXYqueue;
3720 std::set<std::pair<int, int>> reachedBinXYs;
3721 binXYqueue.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3722 reachedBinXYs.emplace(binIdX, binIdY);
3723
3724 while (binXYqueue.size() > 0)
3725 {
3726 std::pair<int, int> curXY = binXYqueue.front();
3727 binXYqueue.pop();
3728 int curbinIdX = curXY.first, curbinIdY = curXY.second;
3729
3730 PlacementBinInfo *curBin = curBinGrid[curbinIdY][curbinIdX];
3731 float bin2TargetXYDistance = curBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3732 if (bin2TargetXYDistance > displacementThreshold)
3733 continue;
3734 int findSiteCnt = 0;
3735 for (auto curSite : curBin->getCorrespondingSites())
3736 {
3737 if (!curSite->isOccupied() && !curSite->isMapped())
3738 {
3739 if (getDisplacement(targetX, targetY, curSite) < displacementThreshold)
3740 {
3741 findSiteCnt++;
3742 res->push_back(curSite);
3743 }
3744 }
3745 }
3746
3747 if (res->size() < (unsigned int)siteNumThreshold)
3748 {
3749 for (int nextY = curbinIdY - 1; nextY <= curbinIdY + 1; nextY++)
3750 {
3751 for (int nextX = curbinIdX - 1; nextX <= curbinIdX + 1; nextX++)
3752 {
3753 if (!(nextY >= 0))
3754 continue;
3755 if (!((unsigned int)nextY < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId].size()))
3756 continue;
3757 if (!(nextX >= 0))
3758 continue;
3759 if (!((unsigned int)nextX < SharedBELTypeBinGrid[sharedTypeId][binIdY].size()))
3760 continue;
3761 PlacementBinInfo *nextBin = curBinGrid[nextY][nextX];
3762 float nextBin2TargetXYDistance = nextBin->getManhattanDistanceTo(targetX, targetY);
3763 if (nextBin2TargetXYDistance > displacementThreshold)
3764 continue;
3765 std::pair<int, int> nextXY(nextX, nextY);
3766 if (reachedBinXYs.find(nextXY) == reachedBinXYs.end())
3767 {
3768 reachedBinXYs.insert(nextXY);
3769 binXYqueue.push(nextXY);
3770 }
3771 }
3772 }
3773 }
3774 }
3775 }
3776 displacementThreshold *= 1.5;
3777 }
3778
3779 return res;
3780 }

4016 inline unsigned int getPairPinNum(DesignInfo::DesignCell *LUTA, DesignInfo::DesignCell *LUTB)
4017 {
4018 if (LUTA->getInputPins().size() == 6 || LUTB->getInputPins().size() == 6 || LUTA->isLUT6() || LUTB->isLUT6())
4019 return 12;
4020
4021 int pinNumA = 0;
4022 int totalPin = 0;
4023 int netIds[5]; // be aware that a LUT might have pins connected to the same net and they should be treated as
4024 // different inputs.
4025
4026 for (auto tmpPin : LUTA->getInputPins())
4027 {
4028 if (!tmpPin->isUnconnected())
4029 {
4030 netIds[pinNumA] = tmpPin->getNet()->getElementIdInType();
4031 pinNumA++;
4032 }
4033 }
4034 totalPin = pinNumA;
4035 for (auto tmpPin : LUTB->getInputPins())
4036 {
4037 if (!tmpPin->isUnconnected())
4038 {
4039 bool matched = false;
4040 for (int i = 0; i < pinNumA; i++)
4041 {
4042 if (netIds[i] >= 0 && netIds[i] == tmpPin->getNet()->getElementIdInType())
4043 {
4044 netIds[i] = -1;
4045 matched = true;
4046 break;
4047 }
4048 }
